{
  "stem": "14429.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a short time thereafter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- I came in March '39, and a year later, that was it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Half a year was in Limburg, and then a very short period.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By then, I spoke French already pretty well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The war broke out, and it was havoc.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father was recognized by the Germans as an alien.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was sent, as an alien, like he would be German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Like he would be German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was sent to Saint-Cyprien, in the south of France, interned there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "German Jews and Austrian Jews were considered aliens in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They made no difference between Jews and non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In a place called Gurs, my father was gone suddenly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shortly after the war started.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Within 10 days, Belgium was occupied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This-- the war started May 10, and a week later, it was-- 10 days later it was occupied.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "France fell a few weeks later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Big, mighty France.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then we got a notification from the Brussels that my brother and I-- Oh.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father eventually escaped there from Saint Cyprien He had forged papers, and he had a lot of guts, and he looked nothing-- not at all Jewish, was a handsome man.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when the Germans went through the train to look at the papers of the people, my father opened his wallet and took some paper, and when he came, he just put it in, as if he'd already shown.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he bluffed his way through, and he went back to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was really a wonderful reunion.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
